svg.title: Normalized Avg Hourly Rides vs Temperature
svg.desc: Line chart with normalized bike ride frequency (y-axis) by temperature in degrees Celsius (x-axis). Three lines represent Subscribers (dark blue), Customers (dark orange), and the Total (black). All lines rise from near 0 at 0°C to peak around 25°C, then slightly decline past 30°C. Customers show more sensitivity to temperature, while Subscribers are more stable.
